trans-unit.source: Defines methods for reading the parts of a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> and also for limited types of writing to the document.
trans-unit.target: 부분을 읽기 위한 메서드를 정의 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> 제한 된 형식의 문서에 쓰기에도 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsSignatureDefinition"></xref> to the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
The definition that is added.
Flushes the package <xref:System.IO.Stream> and also commits an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsSignatureDefinition"></xref> to the package.
Gets the zero-based position of the document in the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
An <xref:System.Int32> that represents the document location in the sequence.
Gets the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""></xref> part, if one exists, of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 가져옵니다는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""> </xref> 있을 경우 파트의 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: An [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] document does not need to have a Document Structure part.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] 문서에서 문서 구조 부분이 포함 될 필요가 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure"></xref> that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""></xref> element, if one exists, and its child elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure"> </xref> 나타내는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_DocumentStructure" name="DocumentStructure" href=""> </xref> 있는 경우 요소 및 해당 자식 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage"></xref> readers, one reader for each page in the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: A collection of fixed page readers, one reader for each page in the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 각 페이지에 대 한 판독기 고정된 페이지 독자의는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reader for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage"></xref> with the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 판독기를 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage"> </xref> 지정 된 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the page.
An <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageReader"></xref> for the page.
Gets the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>, if one exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.

For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] document, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 자세한 내용은 <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>의 일부로 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] 문서, 2 장 참조는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 사양에서 얻을 수 있는 [XPS: 사양 및 라이선스 다운로드](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that contains the default printing options for the document; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if no print ticket exists for the document.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> 문서;에 대 한 기본 인쇄 옵션을 포함 하는 또는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> 없는 인쇄 티켓 문서에 있는 경우.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsSignatureDefinition"></xref> from the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
The definition that is removed.
Gets a collection of all the signature definitions that are associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 연관 된 모든 서명 정의의 컬렉션을 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection%601> of signature definitions, typically one for every person who signed or will sign the document.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection%601> 모든 사람에 게 문서에 서명 하거나 서명 하나에 일반적으로 서명 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the thumbnail image, if a thumbnail exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 연결 된 미리 보기 있는 경우 미리 보기 이미지를 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsThumbnail"></xref> that represents the image.
Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.
A <xref:System.Uri> that represents the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the document.
